trans-unit.source: Deriving PartialEq implements the eq method. When PartialEq is derived on structs, two instances are equal only if all fields are equal, and the instances are not equal if any fields are not equal. When derived on enums, each variant is equal to itself and not equal to the other variants.
trans-unit.target: 派生 PartialEq 实现 eq 方法。当 PartialEq 在结构上派生时，两个实例仅在所有字段均相等时才相等，而在任何字段不相等时则实例不相等。当从枚举派生时，每个变体等于其自身，而不等于其他变体。

trans-unit.source: Deriving PartialOrd implements the partial_cmp method, which returns an Option<Ordering> that will be None when the values given don’t produce an ordering. An example of a value that doesn’t produce an ordering, even though most values of that type can be compared, is the not-a-number (NaN) floating point value. Calling partial_cmp with any floating point number and the NaN floating point value will return None.
trans-unit.target: 派生 PartialOrd 实现了 partial_cmp 方法，该方法返回 Option<Ordering> ，当给定的值不产生排序时，该选项将为 None 。即使可以比较该类型的大多数值，也不会产生排序的值的一个示例是非数字（ NaN ）浮点值。调用带有任何浮点数和 NaN 浮点值的 partial_cmp 将返回 None 。

Dispatch is the mechanism to determine which specific version of code is actually run when it involves polymorphism. Two major forms of dispatch are static dispatch and dynamic dispatch. While Rust favors static dispatch, it also supports dynamic dispatch through a mechanism called ‘trait objects’.
trans-unit.target: 调度是一种机制，用于确定涉及多态性时实际运行哪个特定版本的代码。调度的两种主要形式是静态调度和动态调度。尽管Rust支持静态分配，但它也通过称为“特征对象”的机制支持动态分配。

Distinct from the Instant type, this time measurement is not monotonic. This means that you can save a file to the file system, then save another file to the file system, and the second file has a SystemTime measurement earlier than the first. In other words, an operation that happens after another operation in real time may have an earlier SystemTime!
